title: Reducing $BSCX Max Supply To 10M
body:
This proposal will give permission for BSCX token hodlers and LP token owners of BSCX/BUSD and BSCX/BNB pairs could participate into the voting process.

The main content for core voting is as below:

To decrease the total supply of BSCX token from 100,000,000 to 10,000,000
Vote YES if you agree to decrease the total supply of BSCX as proposed.

Reference: https://bscex.org/core-voting-proposal-for-reducing-bscxs-total-supply-from-100000000-to-10000000/
author: 0x4dA2685A8359E8193e5CBF147525487940ffb8b1
